%% Diagram: Presence Pipeline
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant GW as Gateway pod
    participant Redis as Redis (TTL state)
    participant PS as Redis pub/sub
    participant SubGW as Subscriber gateways
    participant Sub as Subscribed clients

    loop every 30s
        Client->>GW: heartbeat
        GW->>Redis: HSET presence:{u} status=online
        GW->>Redis: EXPIRE presence:{u} 120
    end

    Note over Client,GW: state change (online/offline/typing)

    Client->>GW: typing.start(convId)
    GW->>Redis: SETEX typing:{conv}:{u} 5
    GW->>PS: PUBLISH presence:changes {delta}

    PS-->>SubGW: deliver delta
    SubGW->>SubGW: filter by subscribed users
    SubGW-->>Sub: presence.update / typing.update

    Note over Client,GW: missed heartbeat (3 ticks)
    GW->>Redis: key TTL expires
    Redis-->>PS: keyspace notification
    PS-->>SubGW: presence offline
    SubGW-->>Sub: status=offline (last_seen=now)
